title: 2015-16 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11
description:
2015-16 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11


included:

- Tool: Selector
* New added Tab: Options
* New added Tab: Performances
* Tab "players":
NEW: full 3d-rotatable player preview of your settings
NEW: added option to put underarmour sleeves, Underarmor Neck (on dry weather) on player
NEW: sort option added: sort by team
* Tab "performances":
NEW: Stadium Lighting Fix - turn on/off lighting fix for new stadiums
NEW: Players Hair Quality - change quality of hair to low, normal, high (files are a seperate download)

- Program: FIFA 11 Patch Updater
Now avaible as seperate program: can be started from start menu


- db
* Squads - rosters: date 30.10.2015, player stats: 17.12.2015 (according official fifa 16 squad update)
* Online & Offline version
* New league: Brazil serie a - not full league: 16 teams, only FIFA 16 teams (for now)
* New national teams: Canada, China PR, Korea Republic
* New promoted teams
* career: update supercup fixtures
* career: update CL/EL final stadium


- kits
* all 2015-16 kits (FIFA 16 + improvements)
* Euro 2016 kits : Spain, Germany, Italy, North Ireland, Denmark, Belgium, Sweden, Wales, Scotland, Russia
* xtra GK kits (random chosen at each match):
 Arsenal
 Everton
 Liverpool
 Manchester City
 Manchester Utd
 Newcastle Utd
 Southampton
 Tottenham (Yellow Kit)
 West Brom
 Real Madrid (Green Kit)

- New balls
* Nike Ordem 3
* Nike Ordem 3 Winter
* Nike Ordem 3 Super Lig 15-16
* Nike Ordem 3 LFP
* Nike Ordem 3 LFP Winter
* Nike Ordem 3 Serie A
* Nike Ordem 3 Serie A Winter
* Nike Ordem 3 EPL
* Nike Ordem 3 EPL Winter
* adidas finale 15 (UEFA Champions League OMB )
* PUMA SERIE B

* + winter balls (for option 'use winter balls' at Selector)
Nike Ordem III - Hi-Vis (EPL, LFP, serie a)
adidas UEFA Europa League OMB (winter)


- New sleeve types 
Following FIFA 16,
a new type of sleeves will be added (on normal/dry weather):
beside the normal "long" and "short" sleeves, some will wear "underarmor sleeves + short sleeves"
for players like rooney, fellaini, Sturridge, Eriksen, ...
--> these sleeves can be assigned to players with the Selector program (ingame not possible)


- shoes
* 185 New/updated shoes (list included in download)


- 14 New GK gloves
* adidas Ace Zone Pro - Solar Red/Black
* adidas Ace Zone Pro - Solar Yellow/Black
* adidas Ace Zone Pro IC (Iker Casillas)
* Lotto Stadio
* Macron Lama
* Mitre Awara Pro Negative
* Nike SGT Premier - Grey/Orange
* Penalty Delta Pro - Red/White
* Puma evoPOWER
* Reusch Re: pulse 
* Select 88 Pro Grip
* Sells Wrap Elite Aqua
* Uhlsport bionik +
* Umbro Neo Pro Shotgun - Orange/Black


- flags
* 740+ updated flags (from 16 )


- adboards:
* Generic adboard updated (for teams with no specific adboard)
* Cups updated: Copa America, UEFA Champions League, UEFA Europa League, ...
* Germany - 2. bundesliga (team adboards)
* Spain - Liga BBVA (team adboards)
* Portugal - Liga Nos (league adboard)
* USA - MLS (team adboards)
* Australia - A-League (team adboards)
* Austria - Bundesliga (team adboards)
* Korea - K League (team adboards)
* Scotland - Premiership (team adboards)


- mini faces
* 20.000 updated from fifa 16


- team/league updates
* Updated logos & names (all licensed)


- Country flags (at menus)
* style updated


- New intro
* Intro movies
No Intro-movie
FIFA 16 - Default
* New startup screens


- game stability/performance
* small improvements in .lua files
* improvements: lowered quality of generic hair types (original fifa 11 quality now) --> better fps/performances
* compressed kits for less disk space (4.5 gig --> 375 MB )

* lightning fix for new stadiums:
there s a fix added for missing lightning for new added stadiums
etihad stadium, brazil stadiums, ...
--> can be turned on/off with selector (off after first install)



+ Features from 2014-15 patch
Removed:
* Music: files can be downloaded seperatly if wanted




Supported languages english, Czech, dutch, french, german, italian, spanish (2X), portuguese, polish, Russian



Installation:
1. install fifa 11 
2. install ea patch (1.01)

3. install 2015-16 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11
* run installer "2015-16 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11 (Part 1 of 2).exe"
* run installer "2015-16 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11 (Part 2 of 2).exe"


Notes
- Selector dont start up (if u have .net 2.0) : copy included "Selector (.NET 2.0 version)" folder content to FIFA 11 folder


Problems:
- crashes, ...: use the "i68 regenerator" (select "take care of edited files..." > go , can take some time)



pls leave your comments if there are any problems
